      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Responsibility\n\nprocess new/unprocessed emails\ndecide grouping and actions\nFunction\n\nfetch unprocessed emails\nextract metadata (subject, sender, thread, snippet, timestamp)\ncompare against existing groups\napply grouping logic:\nvector similarity\nstructural heuristics\nAI fallback only for ambiguous cases\ncreate/update groups\nmark processed emails\nperform any archive/label actions",
      "fontSize": 12.051031808751818,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Responsibility\n\nprocess new/unprocessed emails\ndecide grouping and actions\nFunction\n\nfetch unprocessed emails\nextract metadata (subject, sender, thread, snippet, timestamp)\ncompare against existing groups\napply grouping logic:\nvector similarity\nstructural heuristics\nAI fallback only for ambiguous cases\ncreate/update groups\nmark processed emails\nperform any archive/label actions",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
